{pageintro}
The Macro {{breadcrumbs}} includes a list of links of recent visited pages.
{pageintro}

Sample:
{code}
{breadcrumbs:maxItems=20}
{code}
Result:
{breadcrumbs:maxItems=20}

Options:
- maxItems: Optional. Default 20. Number of items.

{warn}
Currently it works only, if {{breadcrumbs}} is always defined with same maxItems
{warn}

Java class: {{de.micromata.genome.gwiki.page.impl.wiki.macros.GWikiBreadcrumbsMacroBean}}.
